| `find`   | Search files by properties | âœ… Yes     | âŒ No  | âœ… Yes           | Deep, flexible searches     |
| `grep`   | Search inside file content | âœ… Yes     | âœ… Yes | âœ… Yes           | Text filtering and analysis |
| `locate` | Name-based file search     | âŒ No      | âœ… Yes | âœ… Yes           | Super-fast name lookup      |

